n          \"priceUSD\": 5,\n          \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-09 01:15\",\n          \"publishStatus\": \"已提交\",\n          \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/04-jwt-token-inspector_SKILL.md\",\n          \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/jwt-token-inspector\",\n          \"gumroadUrl\": null,\n          \"monetizationStatus\": \"待上线\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"name\": \"sql-formatter\",\n          \"description\": \"Format, beautify, and validate SQL queries with syntax highlighting support.\",\n          \"marketRationale\": \"SQL美化是数据库开发和维护的常规需求，统一代码风格有价值\",\n          \"category\": \"database-tools\",\n          \"priceUSD\": 4,\n          \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-09 01:15\",\n          \"publishStatus\": \"已提交\",\n          \"githubPath\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills/blob/main/05-sql-formatter_SKILL.md\",\n          \"clawhubUrl\": \"https://clawhub.com/skills/sql-formatter\",\n          \"gumroadUrl\": null,\n          \"monetizationStatus\": \"待上线\"\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ],\n  \"stats\": {\n    \"totalGenerated\": 30,\n    \"totalPublished\": 30,\n    \"totalFailed\": 0,\n    \"totalBatches\": 5,\n    \"lastUpdated\": \"2026-03-09 01:16\",\n    \"lastSkillName\": \"sql-formatter\",\n    \"totalSKUs\": 30,\n    \"totalRevenuePotential\": \"$135+/sale\",\n    \"gumroadProducts\": 4\n  },\n  \"config\": {\n    \"targetRepo\": \"https://github.com/LeonardoDpanda/clawhub-skills\",\n    \"publishChannels\": [\"webchat\", \"telegram\", \"email\"],\n    \"schedule\": \"0 17 * * *\",\n    \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773076995678}}
{"type":"message","id":"44a45607","parentId":"0ae92d5e","timestamp":"2026-03-09T17:23:28.504Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我已经了解了skill-auto-publisher的工作流程和当前的skill-registry状态。当前已经有30个Skills被生成。我需要按照流程执行每日批量生成任务：\n\n1. 市场分析 - 识别5个高价值机会\n2. 生成5个SKILL.md文件\n3. 推送到GitHub仓库\n4. 发布到ClawHub\n5. 创建Gumroad产品\n6. 更新registry\n7. 记录日志\n\n让我开始执行这个任务。首先进行市场分析，识别5个高价值机会。基于已有的Skills，我需要选择不重复的、有明确变现潜力的开发者工具方向。\n\n已有的Skills包括：\n- config-format-converter\n- batch-file-renamer\n- qr-code-tool\n- rest-api-tester\n- timestamp-converter\n- password-generator\n- csv-data-analyzer\n- url-shortener-expander\n- text-diff-comparator\n- json-schema-validator\n- csv-processor\n- markdown-formatter\n- system-health-check\n- url-encoder\n- meeting-summarizer\n- data-format-converter\n- website-monitor\n- rest-api-tester-pro\n- regex-tester\n- color-code-converter\n- base64-toolkit\n- jwt-token-inspector\n- sql-formatter\n\n我需要选择5个新的、有变现潜力的开发者工具方向：\n\n1. **ssl-certificate-checker** - SSL证书监控和检查工具，开发者运维刚需，可以检查证书过期时间、颁发者、有效性等\n\n\n2. **http-headers-analyzer** - HTTP响应头分析工具，安全检查和性能优化必备，开发者日常使用频率高\n3. **cron-expression-parser** - 解析和生成Cron表达式，简化定时任务配置，DevOps团队常用功能\n4. **docker-compose-validator** - 验证Docker Compose文件语法和最佳实践，容器化部署的核心检查工具\n5. **json-path-query** - 通过JSONPath语法查询和提取JSON数据，API数据处理的关键技能\n\n现在开始生成这些Skills的SKILL.md文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在开始执行每日Skill批量生成任务。当前已有30个Skills，今天将生成第6批（31-35）。\n\n## 第一步：市场分析 - 识别5个高价值机会\n\n基于已有Skills分析和市场需求，选择以下5个方向：\n\n| # | Skill名称 | 市场理由 | 定价 |\n|---|----------|---------|------|\n| 1 | **ssl-certificate-checker** | SSL证书监控是运维刚需，检查过期时间、颁发者、安全性 | $5 |\n| 2 | **http-headers-analyzer** | HTTP头分析是安全检查和性能优化必备工具 | $4 |\n| 3 | **cron-expression-parser** | Cron表达式解析是DevOps和开发者高频需求 | $3 |\n| 4 | **docker-compose-validator** | Docker Compose验证是容器化部署核心需求 | $6 |\n| 5 | **json-path-query** | JSONPath查询是API数据处理关键技能 | $5 |\n\n现在开始生成5个SKILL.md文件："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /workspace/projects/workspace/skills_batch"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":10067,"output":651,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20702,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773076995681}}
